parameters:
MasamuneCan't pass through because it's in the
way. No, it's not just that.

MasamuneI can't even touch the magic barrier.
It doesn't seem possible to force my way through.

Since I tend to forget things easily, I've
decided to keep a diary.

I have written down passwords and important
information that should not be forgotten, so even
if someone other than me finds it, please do not
read it.

Skeleton Head I've never seen this before. It
must be a secret passage.

Skeleton Head It must lead to the girls'
dormitory!
Masamune You still don't know, huh?

Skeleton Head You're such a pervert... Sneaking
into the girls' changing room all by yourself.

Tommy Chachamaru doesn't do such perverted
things.

Skeleton Head I wonder. I always thought you
were wandering around the boys' dormitory, but
you've been hiding a place like this.

Skeleton Head Let's start exploring right
away!
